FormListWidget

public FormListWidget(FormRowHandler<K,R> rowHandler)
Creates a new FormListWidget using the given rowHandler. Note that rowHandler must not be null.

Parameters:
rowHandler - The row handler to be used with this FormListWidget.

FormListWidget

public FormListWidget(FormRowHandler<K,R> rowHandler,
                      FormListModel<R> listModel)
Creates a new FormListWidget using the given rowHandler and listModel. Note that rowHandler must not be null. The listModel can be used to fill the form with rows.

Parameters:
rowHandler - The row handler to be used with this FormListWidget.
listModel - An object that implements FormListModel and provides the rows to this FormListWidget.
See Also:
ListFormListModel, ListWidgetFormListModel, MapFormListModel
